originalText.text:
This doctor listens carefully and knows the human body very well.
As a patient, I became ill and went to emergency room and when the doctors there contacted him he was able to rectify my situation over a phone conversation with them. They had no idea what was happening with my heart; did not know what to do until they spoke to him.
This saved me an overnight stay in the hospital and I recouperated at home in comfort.
He is every bit of excellence if you are seeking a doctor.

Thank You Dr. Bradshaw
